data.description: 5001 Carrington Place is a sophisticated & luxurious retreat that reflects a merging of repose & architecture. Custom created, this estate is a masterpiece of craftsmanship featuring in-lay marble, Quartersawn oak and curly maple trim, white oak floors, sculptural ceilings, tiffany lighting, 7 geothermal units, plus an elevator to transport from floor to floor. The grand entryway w/ a sweeping staircase draws you into a voluminous layout made for entertaining. The 2-story great room w/ French doors to the rear deck is the dramatic focal point of the main level, accompanied by an elegant dining room, kitchen, family room, in-home theatre, gym, & expansive workshop. The master suite features a private terrace overlooking the countryside & an ensuite bath w/ a soaking tub & shower. Sprawling spaces flow outside to multiple balconies & patios, a crystal pool, fire pit & endless greenery beyond. Up to 3 horses allowed on 5.1 acres of premier property with a view!
